PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,FAdditional reporting by Senior
OL,8,FPolitics Producer Lili Donlon-
OL,9,FMansbridge and Investigations Producer
OL,10,FMariah Cooper.
OL,12,FMore than a hundred charities have
OL,13,Fcalled for "urgent" law change to
OL,14,Fprotect the rights of vulnerable
OL,15,Fpeople in care to see their loved ones.
OL,17,FIt comes as an ITV News investigation
OL,18,Ffinds more families of people with
OL,19,Flearning disabilities are claiming
OL,20,Ftheir visiting rights were restricted
OL,21,Fafter complaining about negligent care.
OL,26,@uD@LOUuD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,FLast month the government promised to
OL,8,F"crack down" on care companies
OL,9,Fimplementing "blanket bans" and
OL,10,Fdisproportionate restrictions on
OL,11,Ffamilies visiting their loved ones in
OL,12,Fcare homes and supported living.
OL,14,FBut leading care charities have told
OL,15,FITV News that change is needed
OL,16,Furgently, and argue that regulations
OL,17,Fthe government are focused on - known
OL,18,Fas Regulation 9A - do not go far
OL,19,Fenough.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@LO]qD@NOUqD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,FIn an exclusive interview, Care
OL,8,FMinister Stephen Kinnock said new
OL,9,Fguidance would be introduced to ensure
OL,10,Fthat existing regulations upholding
OL,11,Ffamilies' visiting rights are properly
OL,12,Fenforced.
OL,14,FHe also revealed that the government
OL,15,Fwas exploring the possibility of
OL,16,Fchanging the law to prevent care
OL,17,Fcompanies from introducing visiting
OL,18,Frestrictions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,FITV News has been contacted by
OL,8,Fhundreds of families who say they have
OL,9,Fbeen restricted or banned by care
OL,10,Fcompanies and councils from seeing
OL,11,Floved ones with learning disabilities,
OL,12,Fafter complaining about the quality of
OL,13,Fcare.
OL,15,FCare Rights UK CEO Helen Wildbore
OL,16,Fwelcomed Mr Kinnock's recognition of
OL,17,Fthe problem.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,FBut she has called on the government
OL,8,Fto go further and faster in
OL,9,Fintroducing new legislation to protect
OL,10,Fthe rights of vulnerable people to
OL,11,Fchoose to have a loved one, often a
OL,12,Ffamily member, legally involved in
OL,13,Ftheir care.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,F"Our advice line hears all too often
OL,8,Ffrom people who are too afraid to
OL,9,Fspeak out, even about poor care for
OL,10,Ffear of restrictions, including being
OL,11,Fbanned from visiting their loved
OL,12,Fones," she told ITV News.
OL,14,F"Sometimes people are already at
OL,15,Fcrisis point when they reach out to us
OL,16,Fand they have already had a ban on
OL,17,Fvisiting their loved one. They are
OL,18,Ftraumatised, distressed, worried about
OL,19,Fwhat's going to happen to their loved
OL,20,Fone when they're not there to support
OL,21,Fthem."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@FO]vD@AOU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,FCare Rights UK - along with a
OL,8,Fcoalition of 108 other charities ` are
OL,9,Fcalling on the government to introduce
OL,10,F'Gloria's Law', which would give
OL,11,Fvulnerable adults who access health or
OL,12,Fsocial care services the right to
OL,13,Fnominate someone they choose to be
OL,14,Ftheir 'care supporter'.
OL,16,FThey argue the new law would both
OL,17,Fprotect the rights of vulnerable
OL,18,Fpeople to have loved ones visit them
OL,19,Fin social care settings, as well as
OL,20,Ftake an active role in deciding their
OL,21,Fcare needs and plans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,F"Visiting is not enough. This (new
OL,8,Flaw) is not about a duty on care
OL,9,Fproviders to facilitate visiting. This
OL,10,Fis about shifting the power," Wildbore
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"We are in a situation where people in
OL,14,Freally vulnerable situations are left
OL,15,Fwithout the guidance and support of
OL,16,Ftheir family and friends when they
OL,17,Fneed them most, and that can't
OL,18,Fcontinue."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@_pmpD@DpnrD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,F"(There is) a kind of power imbalance
OL,8,Fbetween families who don't know where
OL,9,Fto go and don't know how to deal with
OL,10,Fwhat's been put in place, and care
OL,11,Fcompanies and sometimes local
OL,12,Fauthorities who seem to hold all the
OL,13,Fcards in these situations."
OL,15,FWe met Mark and Majorie at their home
OL,16,Fin Belfast. Almost as soon as we
OL,17,Farrived, Majorie received a call. It
OL,18,Fwas from her daughter, Laura.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@BpmoD@KpnuD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,FLaura is an adult with complex
OL,8,Flearning disabilities who is currently
OL,9,Fliving in a mental health hospital
OL,10,Fafter being detained under the Mental
OL,11,FHealth Order NI.
OL,13,FLaura called her mum because she had
OL,14,Flost her gloves, and wasn't quite sure
OL,15,Fwhen she might find them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,F"How's my wee woman?" says Majorie.
OL,8,FThey have a short conversation about
OL,9,Fwhere the gloves might be, then the
OL,10,Fcall is over: "Alright, love you, bye
OL,11,Fnow". Laura's life is the story of a
OL,12,Fbroken care system.
OL,14,FShe spent 17 years living in Muckamore
OL,15,FAbbey Hospital, an institution in
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland now subject to a
OL,17,Fpublic inquiry and police
OL,18,Finvestigation after the uncovering of
OL,19,Fa horrific litany of physical abuse
OL,20,Fand neglect of the disabled adults
OL,21,Fthat lived there.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@UO]rD@OOUsD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,FFrom Muckamore, Laura was moved to a
OL,8,Fsupported living facility called The
OL,9,FMews, run by the Cedar Foundation. It
OL,10,Fwas there that Mark and Majorie allege
OL,11,Fthey were blocked from seeing their
OL,12,Fdaughter after raising concerns about
OL,13,FLaura's care and the state of the
OL,14,Faccommodation.
OL,16,FFor a family coming to terms with the
OL,17,Ftrauma of institutional abuse, this
OL,18,Ffelt devastating.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,F"From September 2024 to July 2025,
OL,8,Fthey didn't take her out. Laura wasn't
OL,9,Fallowed out." Mark explains.
OL,11,F"Laura's state was deteriorating. Her
OL,12,Fmental health was deteriorating. Lying
OL,13,Fin bed all day plus the dirt of the
OL,14,Fapartment, the food hygiene, the
OL,15,Ffridge, the washing machine.
OL,16,FEverything we found fault with."
OL,18,F"When they stopped taking her out, she
OL,19,Fjust went downhill. She just wasn't
OL,20,Fbeing cared for," adds Marjorie.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@MO]sD@AOUxD@`O]zD@AOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,F"And when we put in complaints, they
OL,8,Fwere starting to exclude us."
OL,10,FLaura lived in her own flat, which
OL,11,Fcarers would access to support her.
OL,12,FThe electronic key fob, which allowed
OL,13,Fher parents to visit her, was disabled
OL,14,Fwithout their knowledge, and strict
OL,15,Flimits were placed on when they could
OL,16,Fvisit.
OL,18,F"They blame everything on the parents.
OL,19,FInstead of working with you and let us
OL,20,Fhave our opinion," Marjorie told us.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@]O]zD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,F"They just treat parents like they're
OL,8,Fthe enemy. They're just treating us
OL,9,Flike second-class citizens, when we're
OL,10,FLaura's parents, and they know how
OL,11,Fmuch we love her and care about her."
OL,13,FMark and Marjorie took their
OL,14,Fcomplaints to the RQIA, the board
OL,15,Fresponsible for regulating adult
OL,16,Fsocial care in Northern Ireland, which
OL,17,Fthen launched an unannounced
OL,18,Finvestigation into The Mews.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,FIn February 2025, the inspection
OL,8,Fraised "serious concerns regarding the
OL,9,Fcare and treatment" of the people
OL,10,Fliving at the Mews. It found evidence
OL,11,Fof restrictive practices, and concerns
OL,12,Fabout staff training, competence and
OL,13,Fskill.
OL,15,FMark and Marjorie hoped the report's
OL,16,Ffindings, which supported their own
OL,17,Fexperiences, would be a turning point.
OL,26,@pD@HOUqD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,FLaura was allowed out for her 40th
OL,8,Fbirthday party. She looked happy and
OL,9,Fhealthy, but six days later, the
OL,10,FBelfast Health Trust detained Laura in
OL,11,Fa mental health hospital, where she
OL,12,Fremains.
OL,14,FMark and Marjorie's visiting rights
OL,15,Fare now limited to two hours per day
OL,16,Fwith the hospital's permission.
OL,18,F"Of course I worry about her. I can't
OL,19,Fsleep at night. It's really bad. I
OL,20,Flove my daughter," Mark tells us.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,F"We've got no power. They've got all
OL,8,Fthe power and we can't do anything
OL,9,Fabout it."
OL,11,FIn a statement, the Belfast Trust said
OL,12,Fit "understands that Laura's family
OL,13,Fare experiencing considerable stress
OL,14,Fand anxiety in relation to her
OL,15,Fwellbeing. We want to again reassure
OL,16,Fthem that Laura's wellbeing is of
OL,17,Fvital importance to us and we will
OL,18,Fcontinue to work with them regarding
OL,19,Fthe next steps in finding the best
OL,20,Foutcome for her.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@JO]tD@DOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31719
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,F"She is being cared for by a team of
OL,8,Fprofessionals whose sole aim is to
OL,9,Fensure she is receiving the level of
OL,10,Fcare she needs at all times. Belfast
OL,11,FTrust will continue to talk to Laura's
OL,12,Ffamily about any issues they want to
OL,13,Fraise."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31720
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,FA spokesperson on behalf of The Cedar
OL,8,FFoundation said: "We are sorry that
OL,9,Fthe family felt unhappy with the care
OL,10,Fand support we provided however, we
OL,11,Fare confident in our position in
OL,12,Frefuting a claim that restrictions to
OL,13,Ftheir access to their daughter was a
OL,14,Fdirect result of them raising concerns.
OL,16,F"We have a record of complaints raised
OL,17,Fby the family, all of which were fully
OL,18,Finvestigated and reported back to
OL,19,Fthem, whilst Laura was living at The
OL,20,FMews.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31721
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,F"In 2024, a Communications Plan was
OL,8,Fdeveloped over a series of meetings
OL,9,Ffrom June to October, involving Mark
OL,10,Fand Marjorie Sharp, our staff and the
OL,11,FBelfast HSCT. This plan was developed
OL,12,Fin response to escalating concerns
OL,13,Fthat our capacity to deliver safe,
OL,14,Feffective, and person-centred care for
OL,15,FLaura and other tenants was at times
OL,16,Fbeing compromised by the behaviour of
OL,17,Fher parents.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31722
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,F"The electronic fob access for the
OL,8,Ffamily was disabled to address
OL,9,Fconcerns of interruptions to Laura's
OL,10,Fpersonal care routine that was leading
OL,11,Fto elevated levels of distress for
OL,12,FLaura and injuries to her parents and
OL,13,Fstaff.
OL,15,F"In April 2025, the Regulation and
OL,16,FQuality Improvement Authority (RQIA)
OL,17,Fraised concerns relating to elements
OL,18,Fof the service at The Mews. None of
OL,19,Fthese were in relation to
OL,20,Fsafeguarding. The report findings were
OL,21,Facknowledged in full."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU}D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31723
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,FThis is not an isolated story. Mark
OL,8,Fand Marjorie are two of many parents
OL,9,Facross the UK who have got in touch
OL,10,Fwith ITV News claiming that care
OL,11,Fproviders have unfairly limited their
OL,12,Faccess to their loved ones.
OL,14,FIn South London, Jade* tells us what
OL,15,Fhappened to her niece since moving
OL,16,Finto a supported living house run by a
OL,17,Fcompany called Rapid Improvement last
OL,18,Fyear. We are changing Jade's name to
OL,19,Fprotect the identity of her niece, a
OL,20,Fyoung woman with moderate learning
OL,21,Fdisabilities and other disabilities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31724
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,FJade has cared for her niece since she
OL,8,Fwas seven years old. She claims her
OL,9,Fvisits with her niece, who now lives
OL,10,Falone with 2:1 care support, were
OL,11,Frestricted after she raised concerns
OL,12,Fabout her care, including unexplained
OL,13,Fcuts and bruises.
OL,15,F"She has unexplained injuries. She
OL,16,Fkept itching and she said it's really
OL,17,Fsore and she named one of the care
OL,18,Fstaff as shaving her private area and
OL,19,Fshe said why did she do that, and I
OL,20,Fsaid I don't know", she told us.
OL,26,@wD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G24/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31725
SC,0025
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,FJade says she alerted Merton Council
OL,8,Fand Rapid Improvement to these
OL,9,Fincidents. She says she has only been
OL,10,Fallowed restricted visits with her
OL,11,Fniece - and that she was frozen out of
OL,12,Fmeetings and information about her
OL,13,Fcare.
OL,15,F"I've been repeatedly denied access
OL,16,Fgoing there. I can hear her inside
OL,17,Fcalling me. And I can't gain access.
OL,18,FVisiting is 4-7pm once a week, with
OL,19,Fseven days' notice per visit", said
OL,20,FJade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G25/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31726
SC,0026
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,F"We get to sit at a kitchen table on
OL,8,Fsome plastic chairs on just like a
OL,9,Fkitchen dinner table with two staff
OL,10,Fpresent, one at one end of the table,
OL,11,Fand one at the other end of the table.
OL,13,F"They've never communicated with me at
OL,14,Fall any visit, I ask them questions
OL,15,Fabout her welfare, her sleep, her
OL,16,Fdiet, I ask the office, they don't
OL,17,Fever answer my calls, they don't
OL,18,Fanswer my emails".
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G26/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31727
SC,0027
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,FIn a statement, Merton Council told
OL,8,FITV News they "strongly refute the
OL,9,Fallegations made".
OL,11,FThey told us Jade's niece is a "happy
OL,12,Fand thriving young woman who is living
OL,13,Fin high-quality supported living with
OL,14,Fa dedicated two-to-one care team"
OL,26,@pD@OOUqD@QO]sD@`OUvD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G27/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31728
SC,0028
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,F"The council has no concerns about the
OL,8,Fprovider, which is rated 'Good' by the
OL,9,FCare Quality Commission. All concerns
OL,10,Fraised by the resident's aunt have
OL,11,Fbeen thoroughly and statutorily
OL,12,Finvestigated by the council and a
OL,13,Fmulti-disciplinary team, including
OL,14,Fpolice, health, advocacy and social
OL,15,Fcare. No evidence has been found to
OL,16,Fsubstantiate the allegations made."
OL,18,F"Our resident is able to make informed
OL,19,Fdecisions about her day-to-day life.
OL,20,FShe has expressed a preference for
OL,21,Fweekly contact with her aunt."
OL,26,@oD@AOUzD@AOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G28/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31729
SC,0029
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,FJade says her niece has expressed to
OL,8,Fher a desire to see her frequently.
OL,10,FRapid Improvement, who runs the
OL,11,Fsupported living facility, told ITV
OL,12,FNews they take "all allegations
OL,13,Fregarding the care and wellbeing of
OL,14,Fthe individuals we support extremely
OL,15,Fseriously. We firmly refute the claims
OL,16,Fof neglect and mistreatment."
OL,26,@xD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G29/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31730
SC,0030
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,F"The person we support receives care
OL,8,Fthrough a detailed, person-centred
OL,9,Fcare plan developed and regularly
OL,10,Freviewed with the local council and
OL,11,Frelevant professionals. She is
OL,12,Fsupported by a consistent team trained
OL,13,Fto meet her needs, with a clear focus
OL,14,Fon her safety, wellbeing, and
OL,15,Fpromoting as much independence as
OL,16,Fpossible in her day-to-day life. All
OL,17,Fconcerns raised have been carefully
OL,18,Freviewed through the appropriate
OL,19,Fsafeguarding processes, including
OL,20,Finvolvement from external agencies
OL,21,Fwhere required."
OL,26,@oD@AOU}D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G30/31
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
