OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31731
SC,0031
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777017944
OL,3,CCalls for law change as vulnerable
OL,4,Cpeople in care blocked from seeing
OL,5,Cloved ones
OL,7,F"These processes have not identified
OL,8,Fevidence to substantiate any of the
OL,9,Fclaims made. We recognise the
OL,10,Fimportance of family relationships and
OL,11,Fany arrangements around visits or
OL,12,Fcommunication are made with careful
OL,13,Fconsideration of professional
OL,14,Fguidance, safeguarding
OL,15,Fresponsibilities, and the individual's
OL,16,Fown wishes."
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
